You can argue that it's perception of other players that we don't have have anything to contribute to to grps till you're blue in the face, but the bottom line is that that is how we are perceived, and in many cases, it's the truth. We don't offer anything a current Planes grp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>NEEDS</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, such as healing, slowing, crowd control, brain candy, etc. We certainly can't take down a PoP level mob fast enough to make us # 1 on the hit parade. With the mob slowed, the melee just has to whack on it a little longer.<br>
