<br>
I'm writing this after a day where I spent 6+ hours, LFG and trying in vain to start one in various PoP 1st tier zones (don't even bother trying the 2nd tier) and all I had to show for my time was a lousy 3% of an AA point. And this is by no means abnormal. I can log my cleric or chanter on, and if I have to wait 15 min. before getting into a grp, it's rare. You want to tell me again how we're not broken?<br>
